## Database Naming (Future Backend)

### Tables & Columns
- **Database Tables**: snake_case (e.g., `clients`, `tasks`, `users`, `client_engagements`)
- **Database Columns**: snake_case (e.g., `client_id`, `created_at`, `next_due_date`)
- **Primary Keys**: Use `id` or `{table_name}_id` pattern (e.g., `id`, `client_id`)

